{"tid":1762580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"想捐錢但又唔知可以捐去邊？","createTime":"2019-11-29T16:34:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T17:13:19.000Z","uid":160795,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1d03d89a8d761fc866538569bf717be30fdae577","tid":1762580,"uid":160795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:34:56.000Z","msg":"想捐錢但除左星火、立場又唔知可以捐去邊？入嚟呢個Channel，Admin會不定期介紹一啲值得課金支持嘅機構、眾籌比大家。<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/HKersFund\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FHKersFund&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY7hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=18068650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/HKersFund</a><br />\n<br />\n#社會研究<br />\n#眾籌<br />\n<br />\n本土研究社<br />\n<a href=\"https://liber-research.com/support-us-2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fliber-research.com%2Fsupport-us-2%2F&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY7hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=4af9583a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://liber-research.com/support-us-2/</a><br />\n<br />\n機構背景(取自機構網站)︰<br />\n於2010年創立，2014年註冊為非牟利組織，以研究和知識介入各類議題，提昇社會整體的研究論述能力。目前團隊有6位全職研究員，薪酬開支，加上各種查冊、買圖、租金、行政、水電、設計、考察、活動，日常營運開支每月約17萬，但現時只有每月約12萬的小額捐款支持，每月持續負債約5萬。<br />\n<br />\n近期亦密切關注「新疆嶺」最新情況，相關報導<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2P3GNOX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2P3GNOX&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY7hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=0a183c69\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2P3GNOX</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2J4q7TH\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2J4q7TH&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY7hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=33a52d50\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2J4q7TH</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2MQbODu\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MQbODu&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY7hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=e2263d0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2MQbODu</a><br />\n(本土研究社亦有持續跟進棕地規劃及政府明日大嶼計劃，可以到本土研究社網站瀏覽)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《民間研究眾籌計劃2020》<br />\n眾籌目的︰<br />\n籌集資金撐起未來五個對今日香港至關重要的研究範疇，包括土地問題、房屋政策、開放政府、食物安全及中港關係。<br />\n<br />\n相關連結︰<br />\n本土研究社網站︰<a href=\"https://liber-research.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fliber-research.com%2F&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY7hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=9182f771\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://liber-research.com/</a><br />\n本土研究社FB︰<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flocalresearch%2F&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY7hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=c1fd472f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/localresearch/</a><br />\n本土研究社Twitter︰<a href=\"https://twitter.com/LiberResearch\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLiberResearch&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY7hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=4481a743\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/LiberResearch</a><br />\n本土研究社TG︰<a href=\"https://t.me/liberinfo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fliberinfo&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY7hWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=64bc4149\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/liberinfo</a>"},{"pid":"da0945d8a9e946d891692ee48b51eb7bd2e00e3c","tid":1762580,"uid":249263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T16:36:31.000Z","msg":"deadline fighter 一齊寫聖誕卡畀英國歐洲議員！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1761460\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1761460</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n拉落去有哂英國address <br />\n依幾日截郵<br />\n幫手寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=upH1Nnkt